title: (Anti-)Minimalism discussion… book review of Marie Kondo coming soon.
description: This is a video from late November, 2016 (discussing minimalism, etc., following up on other videos that were current at the time).  Yeah, in November, in Kunming, it really was cold enough to be wearing so many layers on camera.  At that time I had not read Marie Kondo's book (title, "the life-changing magic of tidying up").  I am now planning to read and review her book on this channel.
